room_title: Escape room "The Great Fairy Escape" by A Great Escape in Salt Lake City
room_description:
Willow, a care-free and fun-loving fairy has been trapped in a cage by an ogre.

In this newly re-imagined version of our original kid-friendly room, you and your team will attempt to 20 minutes to solve puzzles, riddles, and other obstacles in order to free her from her cage. A great room for beginners and younger audiences.
